name: Frog goes BRRRRRR
description:
This game was entirely created during the GameJam "Mini Jam 106: Frogs" by Mindscore, Koanplan and LauraMarsoner.

The goal was to create a game with the theme "Frogs" and the limitation "Limited time".

Assets

All assets were created during the GameJam by Mindscore except the sound effects which were taken from freesounds.
